import { Grid } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

export default function Center() {
    return (
        <Grid
            container
            direction="column"
            align="center"
            justify-content="center"
            sx={{ minHeight: "100vh" }}>
            <Grid item xs={1}>

            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    )
}
